{"tid":137663,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲唔要焗爐可以讓比小妹","createTime":"2017-02-28T03:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T13:32:39.000Z","uid":51915,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a085989a359fa4cacf330be33498d613bb51fc","tid":137663,"uid":51915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買焗爐 <br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買焗爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我黎緊想去讀甜品 買個焗爐幾百蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾百蚊食到一個星期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge二手焗爐讓出黎 <br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外 <br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有個焗到蛋糕/曲奇ge焗爐 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2f0a46a65de306ef665164c50c82179ed91314","tid":137663,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:59:52.000Z","msg":"做part time啦 一陣買咗個二手焗爐又壞到時你點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377c07992eb25f0ce4015e1f0ee2ec5163d2df7f","tid":137663,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"睇過啦"},{"pid":"523a185455cfd59a917e84d04edeea5893c71d3c","tid":137663,"uid":38874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f273d62f92a7c666369af8444a4b0ca61572b897","tid":137663,"uid":45080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:27:36.000Z","